{"tid":729327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【返墨西哥團聚】留下小孩或一起走    非法移民父母面臨遣返抉擇","createTime":"2018-07-04T12:39:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T16:43:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac036d229c9eb2e4d97355c1b73fe2b706dbfca0","tid":729327,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180704/large/1530688342_1dea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180704%2Flarge%2F1530688342_1dea.jpg&h=a1472434&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國移民及海關執法局（Immigration and Customs Enforcement, 下稱ICE）遭踢爆，要求非法移民填寫表格二選一，要不與孩子一同被遣返，要不自己被遣返而留下孩子。由於非法移民有權向法院尋求庇護，ICE做法被批評把孩童當做人質，強迫移民放棄尋求庇護權。<br />\n<br />\n美國全國廣播公司報道，ICE🇨🇳人員🇨🇳收到上級指示，要求非法移民在表格上二選一簽名。一個選項是：「我要求與我的孩子團圓，並自願接受遣返回我的母國」；另一選項則是：「我在肯定、知情和自願的情況下，要求回到母國，不與孩童團聚。而他們將會留在美國尋求團體援助。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普政府早前推出「零容忍」移民政策，強行把非法移民骨肉分離，引發批評，最終他簽署行政命令中止這項政策。然而，許多先前已被拆散的家庭，至今仍無法團圓。<br />\n<br />\nNBC在報導中引用法令指出，儘管這些移民被當局拘捕，但無論是否面臨遣返，他們都有權利提出庇護申請。兒童法律公益團體「Kids in Need of Defense」炮轟，ICE的做法是把小孩當作人質，強迫這些移民父母放棄原本享有的庇護權利。<br />\n<br />\n美國全國廣播公司"},{"pid":"0f56de03f868e334501c10e5ca8c2801ab993ff6","tid":729327,"uid":35870,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩問題<br />\n你本身就係非法移民"},{"pid":"4e2434be84d3dcca6c122adaf7a6bb54fe57194c","tid":729327,"uid":78304,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:44:44.000Z","msg":"香港都應該咁對果150件"},{"pid":"3cba51f27cf7d8bd71b7f6cb84f8543948734ddb","tid":729327,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:44:55.000Z","msg":"Remember me<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e22eefb393d592c4eb841b1a5c05411e427b3c","tid":729327,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T12:46:08.000Z","msg":"好似係啲非法移民用家庭團聚同個仔做人質喎"},{"pid":"ad461a34890253c04e19dc2f23d75cf1c6b80699","tid":729327,"uid":176366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:35:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做得好"},{"pid":"5bb9a9500f3b4f43726017e0bca88bfc53f32877","tid":729327,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"正 依招屈機"},{"pid":"d4d84b4cb76acf61efc516e9204bbcadf901f67c","tid":729327,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5bb9a9500f3b4f43726017e0bca88bfc53f32877","tid":729327,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"正 依招屈機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:42:38.000Z","msg":"將個問題交返比佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f018219f34a3ea88e4202da15eddd362845f62de","tid":729327,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T16:43:54.000Z","msg":"香港市民都要對150政策「零容忍」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}